Sword
Energy sword
key0=Sword with a very sharp energy coating. Can convert energy using functional modules. You can adjust the hardness of the coating (from 1 to 4), but the more stiffness, the more energy will be wasted. RMB in hand - turn on/off the sword. Shift + RMB - will open the sword interface. The sword can be fed from a field, a condenser and an implant. The stock of the sword battery is 500000 RF. Each unit of power of the sword increases its damage by 5. Each unit of power increases the energy consumption when struck by 1000 RF. Also all installed {"modules"modules} in the sword also spend energy
